# Virtual Machine module (Azure Linux)

This Terraform module creates a **Linux virtual machine** on Azure: optional public IP, managed NIC, Ubuntu (by default) marketplace image, SSH key authentication, and optional system-assigned identity.

For **AWS EC2**, see `Aws/EC2`. For **GCP**, see `Gcp/ComputeEngine`.

## Features

- **`azurerm_linux_virtual_machine`** with SSH keys (password auth disabled)
- **NIC** on your subnet; optional **Standard public IP**
- **OS disk** — size, SKU, caching
- **Image** — defaults to Ubuntu 22.04 LTS (Gen2); override with `source_image_reference`
- **Optional** availability zone, custom data (Base64), system-assigned identity
- **Tags** — `environment`, `managed_by`, and your tags

Network security groups / NSG rules are **not** included; attach an NSG to the subnet or NIC in the root module for production.

## Usage

```hcl
module "vm" {
  source = "git::https://github.com/saurabhrsahu/terraform-modules.git//Azure/VirtualMachine?ref=main"

  resource_group_name = azurerm_resource_group.example.name
  location            = azurerm_resource_group.example.location
  vm_name             = "app-01"
  subnet_id           = azurerm_subnet.apps.id

  ssh_public_keys = [
    "ssh-rsa AAAAB3...comment user@host",
  ]

  create_public_ip = false
  environment      = "dev"
}
```

The root module must configure **`provider "azurerm"`** with `features {}` and authentication.

## Inputs

| Name | Description | Type | Default | Required |
|------|-------------|------|---------|:--------:|
| `resource_group_name` | Resource group name | `string` | n/a | yes |
| `location` | Azure region | `string` | n/a | yes |
| `vm_name` | VM name | `string` | n/a | yes |
| `subnet_id` | Subnet ID | `string` | n/a | yes |
| `vm_size` | VM SKU | `string` | `"Standard_B2s"` | no |
| `admin_username` | Linux admin user | `string` | `"azureuser"` | no |
| `ssh_public_keys` | SSH public key strings | `list(string)` | n/a | yes |
| `source_image_reference` | Marketplace image object | `object` | Ubuntu 22.04 Gen2 | no |
| `os_disk_size_gb` | OS disk size | `number` | `32` | no |
| `os_disk_storage_account_type` | Disk SKU | `string` | `"Premium_LRS"` | no |
| `os_disk_caching` | Disk caching | `string` | `"ReadWrite"` | no |
| `create_public_ip` | Attach public IPv4 | `bool` | `false` | no |
| `availability_zone` | Zone `"1"`/`"2"`/`"3"` or null | `string` | `null` | no |
| `custom_data` | Startup payload (**Base64**) | `string` | `null` | no |
| `enable_system_assigned_identity` | System-assigned identity | `bool` | `false` | no |
| `environment` | dev / stage / prod | `string` | `"dev"` | no |
| `tags` | Extra tags | `map(string)` | `{}` | no |

## Outputs

| Name | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `vm_id` | VM resource ID |
| `vm_name` | VM name |
| `private_ip_address` | Private IP |
| `public_ip_address` | Public IP if enabled |
| `network_interface_id` | NIC ID |
| `system_assigned_identity_principal_id` | MI principal id if enabled |
| `summary` | Short summary |
| `connection_info` | SSH host hints |

## Requirements

| Name | Version |
|------|---------|
| terraform | >= 1.3.0 |
| azurerm | >= 4.0.0, < 5.0.0 |
